							<h1>
							Oregon Administrative Rules (OARs)</h1>
							<div id="ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_ctl00_label" style='display:none'>Page Content</div><div id="ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_ctl00__ControlWrapper_RichHtmlField" class="ms-rtestate-field" style="display:inline" aria-labelledby="ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_ctl00_label"><h2>​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​Access Oregon Adminis​tr​ative Rules Da​tabase (OARD)​<br></h2><div> Welcome to the database for the Oregon Administrative Rules. You have all the rules and filings for Oregon in one easy to search location.&#160;<br></div><div class="oar-access"><div class="span3 search"><h3>Public Access<br></h3> Search rules by chapter or rule number, or search filings.<a href="/archives/Pages/search-oars.aspx" class="button js-button" role="button">Search OARs</a></div><div class="span3 file"><h3>Agency Access<br></h3> Submit filings and minor corrections to rules. 
      <a href="https&#58;//secure.sos.state.or.us/oim/security?oimAction=login" class="button js-button" role="button" target="_blank">Log in to OARD</a> </div> 
   <br style="clear&#58;left;"> ​ 
   <div class="elections-button-grid"><div class="elections-button-grid-item elections-button-doubleline">
         <a href="/archives/Pages/oard-filing-resources.aspx">OARD Filing Resources</a></div><div class="elections-button-grid-item elections-button-doubleline">
